|2nd|suggestion
|3rd|Ashardalon's Stride
|4th|Phantasmal Killer
|5th|Geas

{width:150px,float:right,border-radius:10px}

**Dispater's Influence:** 

The heritiage you have from your fiendish blood is heavily influenced by Dispater's influence. Regardless of your class, Dispater spells are always concidered an option for you to take. You do not automaticly know them, but they are added to the spell list for any class you take.

